				},
				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "This sounds pretty straightforward, but it’s hard to do. Candor is hard when you are still in disaster recovery mode, and keeping calm in these situations is a rare skill<sup><a href=\"#1\">1</a></sup>. Nonetheless, if you can’t write a good report (yet), don’t do it. I’d rather have a late post-mortem than a bad one."
			},
