				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "Oh, and lastly: when I encounter a company that does not have a record of past incidents beyond tribal knowledge, this is a red flag, both in DD contexts and in my consultancy work. You need to track what happened to learn from it."
