				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "I can’t write your post-mortem for you, so I’ll instead give you some things that I’ve used in the past to make my own post-mortems a bit better. I will assume that candor and good technical writing are a given, or at least fall out of scope of this blog post. It’s an important and undertrained skill, but I cannot give you a cheat sheet for it here."
